            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your<strong> ground smoked paprika</strong> to a plate with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong> to the plate and turn them several times in the spices until they’re nicely coated</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
